						\color{darkblue}
						\sffamily
						

\par\textbf{The name of God}

Like English, Hebrew has a word that can mean God or any old god or gods.  The God of Israel also has a personal name, which appears in English Bibles as LORD in all capital letters. 
						\end{minipage}
					}
				\end{wrapfigure}
